	(435,1,'2012-12-05 14:54:05','2012-12-05 14:54:05','May 30th 2012 02:00PM and available for one year on line-Free Webinar (click link below).\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://event.on24.com/eventRegistration/EventLobbyServlet?target=registration.jsp&amp;eventid=453875&amp;sessionid=1&amp;key=5CA8660D0F5BCDCC5D336AAC8CF40D80&amp;sourcepage=register\">Interoperable Integrated Systems</a>\r\n\r\nRegister today and get a link to the archived event available next week and for a full year.\r\n\r\nThere are many security and operational challenges in today’s environment that one solution simply cannot address. Software development kits and the Open Network Video Interface Forum standard make it easier for solution providers to integrate the latest available technologies. The benefit is offering innovative solutions and faster and shorter development and implementation cycles using known technology, tools and standards.\r\n\r\nAttendees may claim one credit toward re-certification of their ASIS Certified Protection Professional (CPP), Professional Certified Investigator (PCI), or Physical Security Professional (PSP) credentials.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about interoperability and integrations, join this webinar and explore how open systems address operational challenges and make it easy to manage security environments regardless of the system architecture.','Interoperable Integrated Systems for Operational Success','There are many security and operational challenges in today’s environment that one solution simply cannot address. Software development kits and the Open Network Video Interface Forum standard make it easier for solution providers to integrate the latest available technologies. The benefit is offering innovative solutions and faster and shorter development and implementation cycles using known technology, tools and standards.','publish','open','open','','interoperable-integrated-systems-for-operational-success','','','2012-12-05 14:54:18','2012-12-05 14:54:18','',0,'http:/