	(447,1,'2012-11-30 01:20:14','2012-11-30 01:20:14','<h2>ASIS International</h2>\r\nASIS International is the largest organization for security professionals, with over 37,000 members worldwide. Founded in 1955, ASIS is dedicated to increasing the effectiveness and productivity of security professionals. We provide educational programs and materials that address broad security topics, such as the ASIS Annual Seminar and Exhibits, and publishes Security Management, the industry’s leading magazine. ASIS is an organization that represents the interests of the security management profession to businesses, the media, government entities, and the public.\r\n<h2>Orlando Chapter 063</h2>\r\nJoining ASIS International also allows members in Central Florida to participate on the local level by joining our ASIS Orlando Chapter. Established on July 22, 1969, we have a long history of security professionals who have made a great impact locally and nationally on our industry.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-13','','','2012-11-30 01:20:14','2012-11-30 01:20:14','',2,'http://127.0.0.1/ASIS_Orlando/wordpress/?p=447',0,'revision','',0),
	(448,1,'2012-12-05 19:35:52','2012-12-05 19:35:52','<h2>ASIS International</h2>\r\nASIS International is the largest organization for security professionals, with over 37,000 members worldwide. Founded in 1955, ASIS is dedicated to increasing the effectiveness and productivity of security professionals. We provide educational programs and materials that address broad security topics, such as the ASIS Annual Seminar and Exhibits, and publishes Security Management, the industry’s leading magazine. ASIS is an organization that represents the interests of the security management profession to businesses, the media, government entities, and the public.\r\n<h2>Orlando Chapter 063</h2>\r\nJoining ASIS International also allows members in Central Florida to participate on the local level by joining our ASIS Orlando Chapter. Established on July 22, 1969, we have a long history of security professionals who have made a great impact locally and nationally on our industry.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-14','','','2012-12-05 19:35:52','2012-12-05 19:35:52','',2,'http://127.0.0.1/ASIS_Orlando/wordpress/?p=448',0,'revision','',0),
	(449,1,'2012-12-05 00:50:49','2012-12-05 00:50:49','<h2><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Employment</span></h2>\r\nIf you are looking for industry professionals to hire, please let us know ASAP and we will post it on our website and include the information in our emails. Members can always check with <a href=\"http://www.asisonline.org/careercenter/index.xml\">ASIS International</a> for job postings  We have a number of links below to help in your search for employment, please check back for additional postings.\r\n\r\n<em>Chairman</em>\r\n<h3>Links</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://asisregion13.com/HOT_Jobs_.html\">Florida Security Employment Opportunities</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.careerbuilder.com/Jobs/Orlando/\">careerbuilder.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jobs.monster.com/l-orlando,-fl.aspx\">Monster.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.careerjet.com/municipal-jobs/florida-374.html\">Career Jet</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.indeed.com/jobs?q=municipality&amp;gclid=CIr7sM_Yq6oCFcO77QoddgQqCA\">indeed.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://florida.jobing.com/\">Jobing.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Employment','','inherit','open','open','','145-revision-13','','','2012-12-05 00:50:49','2012-12-05 00:50:49','',145,'http://127.0.0.1/ASIS_Orlando/wordpress/?p=449',0,'revision','',0),
